{"tid":770753,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴大股東尋求買斷球隊股權","createTime":"2018-08-07T11:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T11:00:14.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"75972642b0946addc982808302401d1ac9f12d74","tid":770753,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:00:14.000Z","msg":"英超球隊阿仙奴大股東高安基(Kroenke)尋求買斷該球會股權。<br />\n<br />\n路透報道，高安基已提出買斷該球隊股權，對其估值約為18億英鎊(約183.23億港元)，此前他已獲得少數股東俄羅斯億萬富翁烏斯曼諾夫(Alisher Usmanov)的支持。<br />\n<br />\n高安基已持有阿仙奴67%股權，他在遞交給倫敦證券交易所的聲明中稱，認為球隊會將從私有化中受益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1909800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1909800&d=CByY6opXVAj6kKRM0DXF1SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=9c1b4365\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1909800</a>"}]}